<font:Arial Bold:16>About The Game: <font:Arial:16>Stig Racing is a racing game revolving around the mysterious 'Stig' character who appears in the television series Top Gear. It is designed to be simple, yet fun, with a number of 'challanges' for players to pick from. Hope you enjoy.

<font:Arial Bold:16>Game Development: <font:Arial:16>The game has been developed as a Masters group assignment for a computer games programming and design unit. The developers and their input to the game are found within the ‘credits’ section found here. Development of the game has taken around 2 months.
 
